name: Pokies!
description:
A LoRA for adding that little bit of extra perk to your gens.

Needs no trigger words to work - just select it in SD settings or add it to your prompt and go! I recommend using it at about 0.7-0.8 strength. Should work with most models - I tested Liberty and Protogen 2.2 and got good results with both. Has a tendency to crop the subject's face out - try adding "selfie" and "cropped" to your negative prompt to reduce the chances of this.

modelVersions.description: Alpha version. Still experimenting with best training parameters and data.
